[Event "Baker Bridge - DONT"]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "1"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "None"]
[Deal "E:KQT6.AQT.JT3.K84 83.KJ82.964.AQ73 J42.9754.A8.JT92 A975.63.KQ752.65"]
[Declarer "N"]
[Contract "2D"]
[Result ""]
[Auction "E"]
1NT pass pass 2D pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 1, chOption: N, chBasis: N, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:0, nBasis: 0, nRot: 0, useStandardVul: true"]
[BoardVersionToken "9c27797ab2d4f7faeccb9436d9700ff44449dad304e418df47665fbf2b05445f"]
[Category "Competitive Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/dont"]
[Student "S"]
{Your hand is too balanced to intervene over East's 1NT so you pass.

Then partner overcalls 2\D.  

Partner has two suits, \Ds and one of the Majors. If his other suit is \Hs then a 2\H bid by you would work great. But if his other suit is \Ss anything you say would not be good.

Since you can tolerate \Ds your safest call is pass.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "N"]
[Vulnerable "EW"]
[Deal "N:A8.AT5.K32.KQ874 T75.KQJ982.A96.3 K9632.63.JT84.T5 QJ4.74.Q75.AJ962"]
[Declarer "E"]
[Contract "2H"]
[Result ""]
[Auction "N"]
1NT X pass 2C pass 2H pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 3, chOption: E, chBasis: S, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:1, nBasis: 2, nRot: 3, useStandardVul: true"]
[BoardVersionToken "9cb37a0f166611056a188b6bf8b2a1e0f5106831e4857a0732a679d6c942f6b0"]
[Category "Competitive Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/dont"]
[Student "S"]
{With 10 HCP and a solid 6-card suit this is an ideal DONT bid. You double and partner follows procedure by saying 2\C.

Now you follow procedure by showing your 6-card suit. You bid 2\H and everybody passes.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "5"]
[Dealer "W"]
[Vulnerable "None"]
[Deal "W:A2.KQ83.Q65.AJ94 T7.AJ9742.A82.KQ K5.T.KJT73.87653 QJ98643.65.94.T2"]
[Declarer "S"]
[Contract "2S"]
[Result ""]
[Auction "W"]
1NT X pass 2S pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 5, chOption: S, chBasis: S, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:2, nBasis: 2, nRot: 0, useStandardVul: true"]
[BoardVersionToken "a14ec074824365e37e4eaca260556fd856056f558e3eff65aa980c7414133dc6"]
[Category "Competitive Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/dont"]
[Student "S"]
{Partner's double asks you to bid 2\C as a relay bid so he can name his suit.

But you don't want him to bid his 6-card suit, your hand is useless unless \Ss are trumps. So ignore the relay request and bid 2\S. Everybody passes.}

